summary: A new Nordic cabin interior and exterior model with some Stormcloak style.
descriptionHtml:
=========================
Stormcloak Cabin Resource
=========================

By Kraeten

=========================
Modder's Resource
=========================

This will be my last contribution to the Nexus community for quite some time, as I'm leaving for basic military training later today. I had so many projects in the works, but sadly this is the only one that I could get finished in time. Hopefully you'll enjoy it! This resource features two new meshes, a interior and exterior crafted completely by myself. They have working collision, and by default they use Windhelm textures. You are of course free to switch that around as you like. I wish you all the best, happy modding everyone!

=========================
Tools Used
=========================
Nifskope
NifUtils by Skyfox
3DS Max

=================
Permissions:
=================

This is a modders resource.You may use the meshes for your own mods as long
as you give credit and you do not charge money for it.

Do not upload to other sites without express permission.

=================
Credits:
=================

The Niftools team for giving us Nifskope.
Skyfox from the Niftools team for his great tool NifUtils
1shoedpunk and Tamira for offering tips and advice to me as I learned how to play around with various 3D applications.
